All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
ChangeBox
The ChangeBox Class represents a Vending Machine's changebox where it contains the Vending Machine's coins and cash.
Factory
This program Simulates a Vending Machine Factory where the user can create a Vending machine of their choice.
Item
The Item class represents the Items that are placed in the vending machines.
ItemLoader
The ItemLoader class represents our chosen items for MCO1 and MCO2.
MainPage
MainPage is the View of our program.
RegularVM
The RegularVM class represents the Regular Vending Machine which contains all of the features of a Regular Machine.
Slot
The Slot Class represents a Slot you would see in a vending machine.
SpecialVM
The SpecialVM class represents the Regular Vending Machine which contains all of the features of a Regular Machine.
SummaryReceipt
The SummaryReceipt class represents a Receipt which contains the transactions, sales, and inventory.
